data.description: Come see this new listing 3 Bed, 2 Bath Home in Creekside, Mulberry, Florida    Welcome to your dream starter home, nestled in the heart of the desirable Creekside community in Mulberry, just off Highway 60 and on the outskirts of Lakeland. This gem is conveniently located near County Line Road, offering the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. This home has 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms: Spacious layout with three bedrooms for your growing family or home office needs. Ideal location just a stone's throw away from Highway 60 and County Line Road, providing easy access to Lakeland and beyond. This home has an Oversized Fenced-in Yard: Enjoy the luxury of a sprawling yard, perfect for family gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding in your own private oasis. Almost half an acre ensures there's plenty of room for all your outdoor activities. Dive into relaxation with the nearby community pool—your go-to spot for cooling off on warm Florida days or if you prefer a more intimate swimming experience you've got your own above-ground pool right in your backyard. You have Ample Space for Toys: Park your boat, RV, or any other toys in the generous yard space—no need to worry about storage hassles. Call for a Private Showing: Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Schedule your private showing today to explore all the features this home has to offer. Seize the chance to make this property your own before it's too late! Your dream home awaits in the picturesque community of Creekside.
